description: Vinny is an extremely athletic guy.He's very adventurous, and says he loves to try new things. He's very lean and trim, and his face has sharp chiseled features that probably cause people to do double-takes quite a bit when they see him for the first time.He's very particular about his women, and quite faithful too. He wants to find one girl who he can focus all his attention (and his talents!) on. That's going to be one lucky girl.
title: Vinny
